Class Dialogs

java.lang.Object
  cs301.group8.blem.Dialogs

public class Dialogs
extends java.lang.Object

Dialogs class handles the creation of dialogs in our Android app. For this version, there are two dialogs, the delete item dialog and the add group dialog.

Version:
1.0
